-Don't mess around.
-It's been two hours.

97
00:07:45,500 --> 00:07:46,420
Why hasn't he come out?

98
00:07:46,580 --> 00:07:48,140
The longer it takes, the bigger his trouble.

99
00:07:49,860 --> 00:07:50,380
Mingming.

100
00:07:51,540 --> 00:07:52,060
Everything alright?

101
00:07:52,580 --> 00:07:53,460
Don't worry.

102
00:07:53,460 --> 00:07:56,140
Uncle Gao said, he has been arrested before for theft.

103
00:07:56,300 --> 00:07:57,300
This is the second time.

104
00:07:57,300 --> 00:07:58,300
The sentence should be severe.

105
00:07:58,300 --> 00:08:00,860
Scum like that are exploiting our legal system.

106
00:08:00,860 --> 00:08:01,930
He thought he wouldn't be caught.

107
00:08:02,260 --> 00:08:02,700
Well,

108
00:08:02,700 --> 00:08:04,300
