119
00:08:19,940 --> 00:08:20,860
Would you like to come?

120
00:08:21,220 --> 00:08:22,100
Animals?

121
00:08:23,100 --> 00:08:23,700
I'm in.

122
00:08:23,780 --> 00:08:24,580
Let's go together.

123
00:08:24,660 --> 00:08:25,300
Fine.

124
00:08:25,460 --> 00:08:26,300
I...

125
00:08:27,020 --> 00:08:27,940
I need to run some errands that morning.

126
00:08:27,940 --> 00:08:28,780
Can I join you later?

127
00:08:29,620 --> 00:08:30,620
Sure, no problem.

128
00:08:31,020 --> 00:08:31,540
No need to hurry.

129
00:08:31,540 --> 00:08:32,419
Safe ride.

130
00:08:34,220 --> 00:08:34,940
Hello.

131
00:08:34,940 --> 00:08:36,100
Welcome to our animal shelter.

132
00:08:36,460 --> 00:08:38,419
Behind me are some gloves, masks,

133
00:08:38,419 --> 00:08:39,740
and sanitizers.

134
00:08:39,740 --> 00:08:41,059
Feel free to use them.

135
00:08:41,539 --> 00:08:43,340
These cages have just arrived here.

136
00:08:43,340 --> 00:08:45,180
We need your help to set them up.

137
00:08:45,730 --> 00:08:47,860
We also need your help in cleaning

138
00:08:47,860 --> 00:08:49,340
the dog houses and cat houses

139
00:08:49,340 --> 00:08:50,940
and give the dogs and cats a bath.

140
00:08:51,620 --> 00:08:53,330
Do be careful

141
00:08:53,330 --> 00:08:55,180
when you are with our little friends.

142
00:08:55,460 --> 00:08:57,220
If you think they are not mentally stable,

143
00:08:57,290 --> 00:08:59,460
please contact our staff for help.

144
00:08:59,780 --> 00:09:00,460
Thank you very much.

145
00:09:03,180 --> 00:09:04,740
You may come here and take the stuff you need.

146
00:09:05,060 --> 00:09:05,540
These are for the ears.

147
00:09:05,860 --> 00:09:06,420
Gloves.

148
00:09:07,410 --> 00:09:07,740
Gloves.

149
00:09:07,740 --> 00:09:08,410
Please give me one more.

150
00:09:08,580 --> 00:09:08,980
There you are.

151
00:09:11,260 --> 00:09:11,810
See you later.

152
00:09:11,900 --> 00:09:12,420
Thank you.

153
00:09:12,740 --> 00:09:13,300
See you later.

154
00:09:15,890 --> 00:09:16,420
Let's go.

155
00:09:16,420 --> 00:09:17,380
Let's take all the useful ones

156
00:09:17,380 --> 00:09:18,180
over there.

157
00:09:18,180 --> 00:09:19,730
I haven't helped anyone take a bath back home.

158
00:09:19,730 --> 00:09:20,580
They should feel honored that

159
00:09:20,580 --> 00:09:21,930
I am doing this for them.

160
00:09:21,930 --> 00:09:22,900
Don't do that then.

161
00:09:23,140 --> 00:09:24,060
What if they are male?

162
00:09:24,740 --> 00:09:25,620
It's okay.

163
00:09:25,620 --> 00:09:26,860
We do it in a different way.

164
00:09:26,860 --> 00:09:27,860
We lick ourselves.

165
00:09:28,380 --> 00:09:29,060
Wait.

166
00:09:30,620 --> 00:09:31,380
Lick what?

167
00:09:33,170 --> 00:09:33,780
Lick ourselves.

168
00:09:35,540 --> 00:09:36,460
Just clean the houses.

169
00:09:37,180 --> 00:09:38,010
Follow me.

170
00:09:39,540 --> 00:09:40,620
Why, Chi?

171
00:09:41,620 --> 00:09:42,380
Why?

172
00:09:44,540 --> 00:09:45,900
Dogs are dogs.

173
00:09:45,900 --> 00:09:47,500
They smell so bad.

174
00:09:47,780 --> 00:09:49,820
Sweetie, you smell so bad.

175
00:09:50,940 --> 00:09:51,700
Here, Xiao Xiu.

176
00:09:51,940 --> 00:09:52,580
Let me take that on.

177
00:09:52,780 --> 00:09:53,620
Luo.

178
00:09:54,660 --> 00:09:55,420
Luo.

179
00:09:55,730 --> 00:09:56,260
Hello.

180
00:09:56,460 --> 00:09:57,490
Why are you here?

181
00:09:58,420 --> 00:10:00,220
I saw your fliers.

182
00:10:00,380 --> 00:10:02,060
I am available this weekend.

183
00:10:02,140 --> 00:10:03,060
So I came to help.

184
00:10:03,460 --> 00:10:05,260
How nice of you.

185
00:10:05,700 --> 00:10:07,490
Well, let me disinfect the place.

186
00:10:19,660 --> 00:10:20,370
What happened to you?

187
00:10:21,060 --> 00:10:21,860
You injured?

188
00:10:23,300 --> 00:10:24,660
It's called Bubble.

189
00:10:25,100 --> 00:10:26,700
It's been rescued for a while.

190
00:10:26,700 --> 00:10:27,900
No one's willing to adopt it

191
00:10:27,900 --> 00:10:29,170
because of its broken leg.

192
00:10:30,420 --> 00:10:31,100
Poor thing.

193
00:10:32,940 --> 00:10:33,940
It's alright, Bubble.

194
00:10:34,890 --> 00:10:35,660
It's going to be fine.

195
00:10:36,740 --> 00:10:37,380
There.

196
00:10:41,660 --> 00:10:42,420
Hold it tight.

197
00:10:46,620 --> 00:10:47,380
Here, Yuanbao.

198
00:10:50,620 --> 00:10:51,290
Feeling good?

199
00:10:57,740 --> 00:10:58,300
You...

200
