203
00:11:08,700 --> 00:11:09,380
You bet.

204
00:11:09,770 --> 00:11:11,580
I have done so many shows about police dogs.

205
00:11:11,580 --> 00:11:12,460
I've got Bulb.

206
00:11:12,970 --> 00:11:14,540
Of course, I am not afraid of dogs now.

207
00:11:16,660 --> 00:11:18,620
There's nothing I can do for you now.

208
00:11:37,060 --> 00:11:37,610
Chi Yan.

209
00:11:38,900 --> 00:11:39,460
Luo.

210
00:11:43,540 --> 00:11:44,420
Thank you so much for coming.

211
00:11:45,140 --> 00:11:46,020
No problem.

212
00:11:49,420 --> 00:11:50,820
Xiao Xiu is really cute.

213
00:11:51,540 --> 00:11:52,540
Just like a cat.

214
00:11:53,540 --> 00:11:54,700
A crazy one.

215
00:11:58,620 --> 00:11:59,060
Now I know

216
00:11:59,060 --> 00:12:00,460
