225
00:12:22,020 --> 00:12:22,780
I used to.

226
00:12:25,260 --> 00:12:26,220
Not anymore.

227
00:12:30,020 --> 00:12:30,940
Because of her, I guess.

228
00:12:38,020 --> 00:12:39,130
I didn't mean to do that.

229
00:12:41,820 --> 00:12:42,900
Take that!

230
00:12:42,900 --> 00:12:43,380
Stop!

231
00:12:43,380 --> 00:12:44,460
Have a bath!

232
00:13:05,460 --> 00:13:06,090
Is it good?

233
00:13:25,300 --> 00:13:27,140
I know we are not doing so well now,

234
00:13:27,770 --> 00:13:30,180
but I thought 
Chi is at least capable of buying food.

235
00:13:37,220 --> 00:13:37,890
It's not what you think.

236
00:13:39,100 --> 00:13:40,620
I just wanted to smell it.

237
00:13:40,620 --> 00:13:41,530
I just...

238
00:13:42,020 --> 00:13:42,780
I just wanted to...

239
00:13:46,860 --> 00:13:48,340
You two smell the same.

240
00:13:50,820 --> 00:13:51,300
Right.

241
00:13:52,260 --> 00:13:52,660
It's the same.

242
00:13:52,660 --> 00:13:55,220
Qin has been getting better

243
00:13:55,220 --> 00:13:56,420
at feeding dogs.

244
00:13:56,900 --> 00:13:58,810
At least I've overcome my fear.

245
00:13:59,300 --> 00:14:00,130
Unlike you.

246
00:14:01,380 --> 00:14:02,940
What? What are you afraid of?

247
00:14:03,210 --> 00:14:04,090
I am a vet.

248
00:14:04,090 --> 00:14:05,180
I am afraid of nothing.

249
00:14:05,180 --> 00:14:05,940
He's scared of frogs.

250
00:14:06,900 --> 00:14:07,820
Frogs?

251
00:14:08,460 --> 00:14:09,250
Frogs?

252
00:14:09,250 --> 00:14:11,260
They are so tiny. Why are you afraid of them?

253
00:14:11,450 --> 00:14:12,100
They are so tiny.

254
00:14:12,100 --> 00:14:12,890
Just this big.

255
00:14:12,890 --> 00:14:13,650
You are huge.

256
00:14:13,650 --> 00:14:14,940
Why are you afraid of them?

257
00:14:14,940 --> 00:14:16,730
Have you got a problem with that?

258
00:14:17,170 --> 00:14:18,660
They are amphibians.

259
00:14:18,660 --> 00:14:20,340
They have legs like ours.

260
00:14:20,340 --> 00:14:21,740
Don't you find it odd?

261
00:14:21,900 --> 00:14:22,780
They also hop.

262
00:14:24,770 --> 00:14:26,460
I...I just can't.

263
00:14:26,460 --> 00:14:28,700
