264
00:14:39,020 --> 00:14:40,290
Morning, my lady.

265
00:14:40,700 --> 00:14:41,900
You are so early.

266
00:14:42,050 --> 00:14:43,180
We are almost finished.

267
00:14:43,660 --> 00:14:44,860
I have brought my card.

268
00:14:45,380 --> 00:14:46,220
You can buy people dinner

269
00:14:46,450 --> 00:14:48,620
and donate the rest to the rescue center.

270
00:14:51,730 --> 00:14:52,290
Mingming.

271
00:14:52,730 --> 00:14:54,260
Ziqi, why are you here?

272
00:14:54,260 --> 00:14:55,300
To join you guys.

273
00:14:57,130 --> 00:14:58,260
This is...

274
00:14:58,860 --> 00:14:59,770
