276
00:15:01,780 --> 00:15:02,290
Xiao Xiu.

277
00:15:02,460 --> 00:15:04,050
This is my sister, Xu Ziqi.

278
00:15:04,420 --> 00:15:05,180
Hello, I am Xiao Xiu.

279
00:15:05,180 --> 00:15:05,780
Hello.

280
00:15:06,540 --> 00:15:07,780
You are really cute.

281
00:15:07,780 --> 00:15:08,980
