290
00:15:28,370 --> 00:15:29,140
Over there.

291
00:15:29,300 --> 00:15:29,860
Yiyi.

292
00:15:31,540 --> 00:15:32,060
Yiyi.

293
00:15:33,060 --> 00:15:33,980
Thank you so much.

294
00:15:34,060 --> 00:15:35,500
You've been of great help.

295
00:15:35,700 --> 00:15:36,660
Safe ride home.

